  <brief_title>The Effect of Supplementation of Flaxseed, Hesperidin, Flaxseed and Hesperidin Together in Metabolic Syndrome</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of Supplementation of Flaxseed, Hesperidin, Flaxseed and Hesperidin Together in Metabolic Syndrome and Its Components: A Randomized, Controlled Study</official_title>
