  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To study the effects of Hesperidin, flaxseed and both together in patients with metabolic
      syndrome, 100 patients will be randomly allocated to one of following four groups: control
      group, hesperidin group (2 capsules Hesperidin), flaxseed group (30 gram flaxseed) or
      flaxseed-hesperidin group (2 capsules Hesperidin and 30 gram flaxseed) for 12 weeks; both
      groups will be advised to adherence the investigators' diet and exercise program too. At the
      first and the end of the intervention, metabolic factors will be assessed and compared
      between groups.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
